name: U.B.A Urban Blockchain Academy Founder (Big DYRT)
description: This NFT is the first of many more to come from The Urban Blockchain Academy. Our goal is to empower the urban community by providing an academy style learning environment for novice artist. Our NFTs purpose is to teach students the main blockchain families and what they represent by imagery and art. The goal of the U.B.A Urban Blockchain Academy is teach and learn the blockchain amongst peers and informative representatives in the NFT/Crypto Space. So if your a novice or a professional there is a spot for you in the Academy.
